OL,3,CMayor and MP in public row over city's
OL,4,Cpothole problems
OL,6,FThe Mayor of and a local Conservative
OL,7,FMP are locked in a bitter public row
OL,8,Fover who is to blame for the lack of
OL,9,Frepairs to potholes in the city.
OL,11,FLabour mayor Ros Jones reacted angrily
OL,12,Fafter Don Valley MP Nick Fletcher
OL,13,Faccused the Labour-run city council
OL,14,Fand the party's South Yorkshire metro
OL,15,Fmayor Oliver Coppard of inaction.
OL,17,FIn a post on X, Mr Fletcher called on
OL,18,Fthe council to "put back in the
OL,19,Fcondition they should be."
