OL,3,CMayor and MP in public row over city's
OL,4,Cpothole problems
OL,6,FHe wrote: "Delay, delay and more
OL,7,Fdelay. It's something we are all used
OL,8,Fto from (Mayor Ros Jones and South
OL,9,FYorkshire Mayor Oliver Coppard) but
OL,10,Fwhy should we accept it?
OL,12,F"Potholes are meant to be dealt with
OL,13,Fby the council. Government provide
OL,14,Fboth Doncaster Council and South
OL,15,FYorkshire Mayoral Combined Authority
OL,16,Fwith a lot of money to do their job
OL,17,Fand provide a good transport network."
OL,19,FIn response Ms Jones said real-terms
OL,20,Ffunding for road maintenance had
OL,21,Fhalved since 2006.
