OL,3,CMayor and MP in public row over city's
OL,4,Cpothole problems
OL,6,FShe said: "Doncaster and councils
OL,7,Facross the country need more funding
OL,8,Ffor highway maintenance. Potholes are
OL,9,Fa blight on our roads and increase
OL,10,Fcosts for motorists.
OL,12,F"As a council we want to be able to
OL,13,Fkeep all our highways in good
OL,14,Fcondition, however 14 years of
OL,15,Freductions in funding from central
OL,16,Fgovernment to local road repair
OL,17,Fbudgets have left many local
OL,18,Fauthorities facing their biggest ever
OL,19,Fannual pothole repair backlog."
OL,21,FWho's really to blame?
