OL,6,FIn a letter published by Mr Fletcher
OL,7,Fon X, transport secretary Mark Harper
OL,8,Fdetails #8.3bn to be given to councils
OL,9,Facross the country for road repairs.
OL,11,FThe money will be delivered over a
OL,12,Fperiod of 11 years, with councils in
OL,13,Fthe North East, North West and
OL,14,FYorkshire and the Humber to receive a
OL,15,Fshare of #3.3bn.
