OL,6,FA Department for Transport
OL,7,Fspokesperson said: "Local highways
OL,8,Fauthorities are responsible for
OL,9,Fmaintaining their road networks, but
OL,10,Fwe are supporting them with the
OL,11,Fbiggest ever increase in funding for
OL,12,Flocal road improvements thanks to
OL,13,F#8.3bn of reallocated HS2 funding -
OL,14,Fenough to resurface the equivalent of
OL,15,Fover 5,000 miles of roads across the
OL,16,Fcountry.
