OL,4,Cpothole problems
OL,6,F"On top of a separate #570m pot of
OL,7,Ftransport funding provided to South
OL,8,FYorkshire Mayoral Combined Authority
OL,9,Funtil 2027, they are also receiving an
OL,10,Fadditional #133m specifically for
OL,11,Froads resurfacing over the next ten
OL,12,Fyears thanks to reallocated HS2
OL,13,Ffunding, with around #2m of that
OL,14,Falready paid and a further #2m to
OL,15,Ffollow later this year."
OL,17,FHowever, according to the Local
OL,18,FDemocracy Reporting Service, Doncaster
OL,19,Ffaces a funding gap of around #150m
OL,20,Ffor highways repairs.
