OL,6,FThe council was awarded around #5m
OL,7,Ffrom central government specifically
OL,8,Ffor these works in 2023/4.
OL,10,FThis is the same figure that was
OL,11,Fawarded in 2010, meaning that real-
OL,12,Fterms funding has halved since 2006.
OL,14,FMeanwhile, an annual survey conducted
OL,15,Fby the Asphalt Industry Alliance (AIA)
OL,16,Ffound that there are around two
OL,17,Fmillion potholes requiring repair
OL,18,Facross the country, the highest figure
OL,19,Fin eight years.
